title: Cafe Prana
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Italian, Raw, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out, Mexican, Bakery, Fusion
description: A 100% vegan/vegetarian cafe offers unique gourmet dishes such as burgers, sandwiches, salads, soups, and noodles. Try the portobello hamburger, portobello tacos, tempeh salads, and pita sandwiches. Also offer smoothies, cold-pressed juices and gourmet coffee beverages to enjoy in the garden.
